msgid "Antenna Temperature"
msgstr "Temperatura antene"

#: src/callbacks.c:137
msgid ""
"Ground plane detected in model. T_ant results will overcount ground effects. "
"Free-space models are standard for antenna temperature evaluation."
msgstr ""
"V modelu zaznana talna ravnina. Rezultati T_ant bodo prekomerno upoštevali "
"učinke tal. Modeli prostega prostora so standardni za oceno temperature "
"antene."

#: src/callbacks.c:153
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Max gain at θ=%.0f° (%.0f° from XY plane). Convention assumes beam in XY "
"plane with observation elevation set by spinbutton."
msgstr ""
"Maks. ojačitev pri θ=%.0f° (%.0f° od ravnine XY). Konvencija predpostavlja "
"snop v ravnini XY z opazovalno elevacijo nastavljeno z vrtilnim gumbom."

