msgid "xnec2c geometry optimizer"
msgstr "xnec2c optimizator geometrije"

#: src/callbacks.c:421
msgid ""
"xnec2c was built without inotify support: the optimizer cannot be enabled."
msgstr ""
"xnec2c je bil zgrajen brez podpore inotify: optimizatorja ni mogoče "
"omogočiti."

#: src/callbacks.c:445
msgid "Xnec2c Optimizer"
msgstr "Xnec2c optimizator"

#: src/callbacks.c:445
msgid ""
"No files are selected for writing. However, xnec2c will still reload and "
"recalculate the input file on modification when triggered by inotify.Select "
"files for writing in \"File->Optimization Settings\"."
msgstr ""
"Nobena datoteka ni izbrana za pisanje. Vendar bo xnec2c še vedno znova "
"naložil in preračunal vhodno datoteko ob spremembi, ko jo sproži inotify. "
"Izberite datoteke za pisanje v \"Datoteka->Nastavitve optimizacije\"."

