#: src/mathlib.c:1034
#, c-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"* Notice: \"%s\" was selected, but you can only change to a\n"
"* different Intel MKL threading library by restarting xnec2c.\n"
"* \n"
"* However, you may continue to select any other Linear Algebra library\n"
"* without restart, including this same Intel MKL library.  All other\n"
"* Intel MKL threading libraries are disabled until restart because of an \n"
"* MKL limitation where the MKL threading library can only be dynamically\n"
"* linked only once per runtime.\n"
"* \n"
"* See Intel's documentation on mkl_set_threading_layer() for more detail.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"* Obvestilo: izbrana je bila \"%s\", a na drugo knjižnico niti Intel MKL\n"
"* je mogoče preklopiti samo z ponovnim zagonom xnec2c.\n"
"* \n"
"* Lahko pa izberete katero koli drugo knjižnico linearne algebre brez\n"
"* ponovnega zagona, vključno s to knjižnico Intel MKL. Vse druge knjižnice\n"
"* niti Intel MKL so onemogočene do ponovnega zagona zaradi omejitve MKL,\n"
"* ki dovoli dinamično povezavo knjižnice niti samo enkrat med izvajanjem.\n"
"* \n"
"* Glejte Intelovo dokumentacijo za mkl_set_threading_layer() za "
"podrobnosti.\n"

